<p>Here it comes! The part where I do a little mini-series on some cool features in Logic Pro X while <a href="/music/2017/12/14/30-days-of-Apple-Logic-Pro-X.html">I spend a month using it</a>.</p>

<p>All three of these are not major unique features, but instead are quality of life-improvements. Little things that other DAWs also do, but not as well or as easily.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Region Based Automation</li>
  <li>Drum Replacement and Triggering</li>
  <li>Guitar Notation and Tablature</li>
  <li>Persistent Undo</li>
</ul>

